name: Zoom meeting link does not end automatically after launch.

inline.description:
1. Click on the Start Zoom Meeting icon on desktop
2. Click on "Join Meeting"
3. Click on "Open Zoom.us" popup in chrome - observe desktop Zoom meeting post as you click
inline.expectedResult: Several seconds later the post in the Mattermost thread correctly shows the meeting as joinable

customFields.Important notes about this step: Note that this test can be run with Zomm configured using any authentication method.
